name: RiggedCoinflip
0:
”Alexa, launch Winning Coinflip”
”Alexa, ask Winning Coinflip to flip a coin”
”Alexa, ask Winning Coinflip to flip another coin”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: winning coin flip
des: Want to always be the winner in those pesky coin flips? This coin flip always lands on heads! Your opponents will be none the wiser as the app is referred to as "Winning Coinflip" in the activation phrases!
